{"tid":1951962,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"補習老師被控管有鐵棒和𠝹刀作非法用途　高院拒保釋","createTime":"2020-03-31T09:50:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T09:50:16.000Z","uid":14454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"eb516a17e3a6babe69a4973776871aebe01e905f","tid":1951962,"uid":14454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T09:50:16.000Z","msg":"去年11月11日有人發起「三罷」，一名男子被控當日在銅鑼灣管有一支鐵棒及一把𠝹刀，被控一項「管有適合作非法用途的工具並意圖作非法用途使用」罪，今日在高等法院申請保釋，被法官陳慶偉拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n被告24歲，是一名補習導師，被控在邊寧頓街及怡和街交界管有這些物品。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1517956-20200331.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1517956-20200331.htm&d=C7qEe2dSMr%2BabA5wG5krtLe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=dd99e51a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1517956-20200331.htm&h=e1ce4fd6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1517956-20200331.htm</a>"}]}